Virginia Grey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Virginia_Grey 0 Virginia Grey (March 22, 1917 – July 31, 2004) was an American actress who appeared in over 100 films and a number of radio and television shows from the 1930s through to the early-1980s.
